data.description: Fantastic starter home just north of Nashville! Recent improvements include encapsulated crawlspace and new ductwork. Aggregate driveway, huge concrete patio in back, plus fenced back yard ready for pets. Nice hardwood floors in living room, kitchen, and all bedrooms. Very large bonus room! 2 HVAC units, approximately 2 and 7 years old.
